aa(lp57
VBut worse still,
p58
aVassemblies of glass towers like this one in Moscow
p59
aVsuggest a disdain for the civic and communal aspects of urban living.
p60
aVRight? Buildings like these are intended to enrich their owners and tenants,
p61
aVbut not necessarily the lives of the rest of us,
p62
aVthose of us who navigate the spaces between the buildings.
